## Regions

Two kinds of comments fence regions in the generated source:

```
// <generated:protected region="...">     ← do not edit; managed by the Foundry
// </generated:protected>

// <llm-editable region="...">             ← LLM patches may rewrite the body
// </llm-editable>                            subject to the typed change ontology
```

The Patch Guard rejects any LLM diff that crosses these boundaries.

